Needed to increase the size of a zFS mounted dataset the other day. I will just provide the link to IBM website for the details but instead of duplicating everthing here, but I wasn&rsquo;t aware this could be done with the pax command instead of the DFSMS REPRO command.
 Snippet example from the IBM site
 //SYSTSIN DD *OSHELL /usr/sbin/mount -t ZFS -f PLEX.OLD.AGGR002.LDS0002 +/service2 ; +/usr/sbin/mount -t ZFS -f PLEX.
